1.0.0.name: wordpress/car-demon-styles
1.0.0.description: Car Demon Styles was developed to work with the Car Demon PlugIn and allows you to change the look and feel of vehicle listings and detail pages. It also provides support for several popular themes like Suffusion, Responsive and CatchBox.
